Notes:
In case you want to switch to the legacy UI (ImageJ 1), you change the dependencies section in your POM to...
<source lang="xml">
<dependencies>
	<dependency>
		<groupId>net.imagej</groupId>
		<artifactId>imagej</artifactId>
	</dependency>
	<dependency>
		<groupId>net.imagej</groupId>
		<artifactId>imagej-legacy</artifactId>
	</dependency>
</dependencies>
</source>

